# Global configuration section
#   Values here are used as defaults for any following Channel section that
#   doesn't specify them.
Expunge None
Create Both

IMAPAccount jack
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User jack@fireworkhq.com
PassCmd "lpass show himalaya-jack --password"
SSLType IMAPS


IMAPStore jack-remote
Account jack

MaildirStore jack-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Maildir/jack/
Inbox ~/Maildir/jack/Inbox
# Clockwise ~/Maildir/jack/Clockwise
# Outreach ~/Maildir/jack/Outreach
# Gmail ~/Maildir/jack/Gmail
# github  ~/Maildir/jack/github
# meetings ~/Maildir/jack/meetings
# salary ~/Maildir/jack/salary
# sentry ~/Maildir/jack/sentry
# slack ~/Maildir/jack/slack

Channel jack
Far :jack-remote:
Near :jack-local:
Patterns * !gmail !monday
SyncState *

